Package: ADCT
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Design in Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yalin Zhu
Maintainer: Yalin Zhu <yalin.zhu@outlook.com>
Description: Existing adaptive design methods in clinical trials. The package
    includes power, stopping boundaries (sample size) calculation functions for
    two-group group sequential designs, adaptive design with coprimary endpoints,
    biomarker-informed adaptive design, etc.
Imports: stats, mvtnorm
Suggests: clinfun, gsDesign
